race.description: Knight Packaging Supplies Mdn Hwt Plate
race.comment: AKARI SPIRIT (6) led them up at Cranbourne over a middle distance and fought on beaten just 1.3L over 2025m at Cranbourne. The Fastnet Rock colt is showing good promise and is ready for the staying trip. In a top barn, and he should have this lot covered. The soft track assists. GRINDING AWAY (3), who's been performing below his best. He's running out of chances, but races forward and will get every chance from the inside gate. He looks the best of the rest. THIBLOS (5) has switched from a South Australia stable on a 13-day return. He's fourth up and the step-up in trip should suit. He has scope for improvement and can get some of the minor purse. ROYAL BEAU (4) is on a quick backup from the picnics but is going well enough to fill the next slot.
